                        "name": "Wrap in Coils",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "<b>Requirements </b>The quetz couatl has a Medium or smaller creature <a aonid=\"20\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">grabbed</a> or <a aonid=\"33\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">restrained</a> in its jaws; <b>Effect </b>The quetz couatl moves the creature into its coils, freeing its fangs to make attacks, then uses <a aonid=\"19\" game-obj=\"MonsterAbilities\">Greater Constrict</a> against the creature. The quetz couatl can hold as many creatures in its coils as will fit in its space.",
