        {
            "name": "Couatl",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Other Couatls",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "The quetz couatl presented here is the most common of its kind, and while most adventurers and scholars refer to them simply as \u201ccouatls,\u201d other kinds exist as well, such as the fierce xiuh couatl, the nomadic auwaz couatl, the wise mix couatl, the nurturing chicome couatl, and the furious tletli couatl.",
